law.text: Any agreement or collusion among lease proposers or prospective lease proposers which restrains, tends to restrain, or is reasonably calculated to restrain competition by agreement to propose a lease with certain terms, or to refrain from proposing a lease with certain terms or otherwise, is prohibited.
law.history: Created 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 54, sec. 12, effective July 14, 1992.
